        "content": "[nnnn]"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Remarks"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "There are three ways to specify how much SPF/PC moves when you"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "issue the command:"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "- Issue the command without a scroll amount.  In this case the"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "SCROLL field determines the amount scrolled.  The SCROLL field"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "is in the upper right corner of the screen."
      },
